==製作==
電影於2015年11月17日在加拿大拍攝<ref name="sd-salt-xyz">{{cite web|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/salt-xyz-enter-horror-the-void/5095980.article|work=Screen Daily|title=AFM: Salt, XYZ enter horror 'The Void'|date=2015-10-27|accessdate=2017-04-05|last=Wiseman|first=Andreas|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225042420/https://www.screendaily.com/news/salt-xyz-enter-horror-the-void/5095980.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本片亦由2015年獲獎無數的電影《[[女巫_(2015年電影)|女巫]]》製片打造<ref name>{{cite web|url=https://www.linjiamm.com/detail/108022/|title=继《女巫》后惊悚颤慄之作！《恐惧虚空》复古 80 年代恐怖电影　扭曲心灵致敬克苏鲁神话！|website=邻家MM|accessdate=2017-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430032431/https://www.linjiamm.com/detail/108022/|archive-date=2019-04-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==發行==
《恐懼虛空》於2016年9月22日在[[奇幻電影節|奇幻電影節]]舉行首映會<ref name="iw-premiere">{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2016/08/fantastic-fest-first-wave-12th-annual-alamo-drafthouse-tim-burton-1201712437/|publisher=[[Indie_Wire|Indie Wire]]|title=Fantastic Fest Announces First Wave of Programming For 12th Annual Celebration in September|accessdate=2017-04-03|date=2016-08-02|first=Vikram|last=Murthi|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308220215/https://www.indiewire.com/2016/08/fantastic-fest-first-wave-12th-annual-alamo-drafthouse-tim-burton-1201712437/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這部電影於10月17日在加拿大{{le|多倫多暗黑影展|Toronto After Dark Film Festival}}首映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://torontoafterdark.com/2016/schedule-and-tix/|publisher=[[Toronto_After_Dark_Film_Festival|Toronto After Dark Film Festival]]|accessdate=2017-04-03|title=First 10 Films Announced! Scary Hit Under the Shadow! Ethan Hawke's Violence! The Void! And more!|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404043759/http://torontoafterdark.com/2016/schedule-and-tix/|archivedate=2017年4月4日}}</ref>。

==評價==
《恐懼虛空》獲得的評價多為正面。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於46條評論，新鮮度74%，平均得分5.9／10<ref name=RT>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_void_2017|title=The Void|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2017-04-07|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111095638/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_void_2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上獲得63分，代表「普遍好評」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-void |title=The Void |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2017-04-07 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204155648/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-void |dead-url=no }}</ref>。多數影評人稱讚電影呈現了80年代低預算電影粉絲對於懷舊的興奮。

《{{le|Screen International|Screen International|Screen Daily}}》的{{le|金·紐曼|Kim Newman}}將本片與導演以前的《Bio-Cop》、《{{le|26種死法2|ABCs of Death 2}}》和《[[激動戰士MAN勃哥|激動戰士MAN勃哥]]》作對比，認為導演是「維持模仿、但淡化了幽默來嘗試深沉的懸念和[[洛式恐怖|洛式恐怖]]-以及令人難忘的可怕物理效果而不是CGI。」紐曼的結論是，電影是「提供了良好的震撼時刻和一個難以預測的情節， 即使有幾個重要關係被粗略地成立，稍微破壞了觀眾對於恐怖的投入。」<ref name="sd-review">{{cite web|url=http://www.screendaily.com/reviews/the-void-review/5114839.article|work=''{{le|Screen International|Screen International|Screen Daily}}''|title='The Void': Review|date=2017-02-13|accessdate=2017-04-03|last=Newman|first=Kim|authorlink=Kim Newman|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404043724/http://www.screendaily.com/reviews/the-void-review/5114839.article|archivedate=2017年4月4日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

